for implementing

00:05:35.950 --> 00:05:39.360
a consistent design
across multiple platforms,

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:43.020
including the web
and native mobile.

00:05:43.020 --> 00:05:46.140
It focuses on bold
colors, tangible surfaces,

00:05:46.140 --> 00:05:48.074
and meaningful motion.

00:05:48.074 --> 00:05:50.490
But we're not going to focus
